Elizabeth Harmon vs Harry Beltik
Netflix Series - The Queen's Gambit
Caro-Kann, two knights, 3...Bg4 (B11)

BUT ACTUALLY:

Rashid Gibiatovich Nezhmetdinov vs Genrikh Kasparian
Spartak Team Ch (1955), Riga LAT
